summary:
Hi, I’m Jordan, I’m 23. I was born and grew up in Andorra. Then lived in Brighton and Amsterdam. I’m native in 4 languages (English, French, Spanish, and Catalan) and learning more (Dutch, Italian and Japanese). 
I am passionate about music, language, ships, and health+fitness. 
I'm qualified to drive boats (under 20m) inland, sailing ships (under 20m) coastal, and to be first mate on a ship.
I also hold a BA Hons degree.
